# No API contracts for this feature.
#
# 011-chat-new-conversation is a frontend-only enhancement to the explorer's
# chat panel (apps/explorer-web/src/chat/ChatPanel.tsx). It adds a
# "new conversation" control and a suggested-prompt empty state. It introduces
# no MCP tool, no backend endpoint, and consumes no new data.egov.bg portal
# endpoint or dataset — so there is no request/response contract to define here
# (Constitution Principle III is not applicable).
#
# This file exists only to keep the contracts/ directory under version control,
# consistent with the Spec Kit feature layout.
